<subSubSection id="1E4BCF7486D0EA8F0CAE23FD61FAB0AD" pageId="null" pageNumber="734" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="0D67659C29BCB0440568E87A8652307E" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Speise-Rhabarber</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="C8B977B0916E10D57D7925D48BC26123" pageId="null" pageNumber="734" type="description">
<paragraph id="51E9362295EDECA781788EB72A0C4149" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">
Bis 1,5 m hoch. 
<normalizedToken id="19F8E45D72CFED5AA184751749A0A854" originalValue="Grundständige" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Grundstaendige</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D2089AC7DC987365B86210778F790C91" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
oval, 
<normalizedToken id="F59965EE3E732FBDF05FA42056F773E9" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">laenger</normalizedToken>
als breit, ganzrandig, am Rande kraus; Blattstiel unterseits ohne Furchen. 
<normalizedToken id="EEBB8BF74FC33C7243167E8886B85F1D" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
nur im untern Teil 
<normalizedToken id="97CF03BAE64C337A884DF16876E4AFD9" originalValue="beblättert" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">beblaettert</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="E9CD732706DDB71DA7871047D0758240" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Blueten</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D9335CDBBBCD1BAAA70C3984E65AB2B3" originalValue="grün" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">gruen</normalizedToken>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="BF007F0425B06676226C2C0B8A8F50E7" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2E7DC7F69009A24829D4B251CA8C91AD" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">
<emphasis id="C39DAF1410F29DB3AAB6B9464F8EE8E3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">
<pageBreakToken id="493632EB5FEB83FD498B004258B4D578" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben. 2n
</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="917B37AC1D60659E03C36D3F65EF9184" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">44:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="7E51835BB980B16C082876C9B42A48D3" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Chin und Youngken 1947, 
<normalizedToken id="027D1F568679D402F33903799C49B06C" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="57C679234750AF02045194F3BFCCD9E9" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="41803693B9BD5E23EF9C92B3AF3EE5B2" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">
<emphasis id="F61C53AF2ED9CC4FA8270F1B5FBEC76E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Standort.</emphasis>
In 
<normalizedToken id="35BECB04438EEF2EDC966F965646A83D" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
als Speisepflanze kultiviert.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="26E3BB372F0B1BDDE849F6C6E87E9283" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">
<emphasis id="CDA5B6FCEAA1CBBDA9F54E025449FB6A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="5526AEDDABE954900809D1A8B84A6E58" originalValue="Ursprünglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Urspruenglich</normalizedToken>
in Nordwestchina, Mongolei und 
<normalizedToken id="EE24AE69C6FE8B52EA579202291516F7" originalValue="Südostsibirien" pageId="null" pageNumber="734">Suedostsibirien</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
In 
<taxonomicName id="B8D378AF1433058417D9B0C337D9269E" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Europa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="734" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Europa</taxonomicName>
seit Anfang 18. Jahrhundert angebaut; kaum verwildert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
